<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-51-1122 </DOCNO><TEXT>The evaporation of two-layered particles with a solid nucleus and a salt-solutionenvelope is examined. The numerical solution of the derived-equationsystem is used to analyze the effect of the internal structure of aerosolson their evaporation, heating, variation of envelope salt concentration,and solid-nucleus growth upon salt rehydration.</TEXT></DOC>